{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "a7c9d0d6-9adb-43c9-bf67-b12f40cb2cea",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 2 07 - Rune Claustra",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "ef940697-031f-42c7-80ec-15a3bf641801",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "90c4bd09-bcdc-4c20-abe2-a6251f1dc3c7",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "591be2a3-9e55-46ea-b4a7-a59f32342eae",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "So far in your lessons on Combat runes and runestones, we have worked with general purpose spells that can be used in any combat situation. They were designed as offensive weapons to damage or disable your oponent.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "fd829614-5f27-4b58-97b0-4a772b6eaf80",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The next two runestones we will make are more specialized. They are defensive tools to be used against a specific type of opponent.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7afc2b0b-ebf1-4217-83c4-67bbbd56558c",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "There are many dangers in the world. As Heroes, you may well face situations where combat is the only recourse. In combat, the most dangerous enemy you will face is one that is already dead.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "055fb829-f6a9-49ad-af18-61ed56933e7b",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The Claustra runestone is implicitly designed to use against Undead, particularly noncorporal ones like Ghosts and Wraiths. This runestone is frequently incorporated into Catacomb design to keep malevolent spirits contained.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f190b96c-6ed8-4691-8f32-50832a03959f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "When a Claustra runestone is placed upon the floor or built into a lintel, Undead trigger the spell when they come into the spell's aura. The Undead are magically blocked and will be unable to move for several moments.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c61c7812-f8ad-4128-afbf-41b82beae8b2",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "To use the Claustra runestone, you must slide the stone across the floor. When the Undead creature passes over the runestone, the spell is triggered and the Undead will be frozen temporarily in place.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "08344a73-e29e-4e31-9252-049f6200942f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "You will be enchanting your own Claustra runestone in this lesson. I sincerely hope that you never have the occasion to put it to use. It is never prudent to confront the Undead directly.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "8637acc7-4bac-4a33-9cf9-335976411ff6",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions or comments relevant to this subject so far?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "2fdca05b-5036-4fd0-af36-7bb367657e97",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "3ae9efdf-887b-46b5-97f9-3c3f8e49517c",
                            "text": "Ask About Undead",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "327dc3a0-3de4-402c-b7ba-3c99c2c0f6ee",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Aren't Undead kind of rare and easy to avoid? Why do we need to make a runestone that only affects them?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e2fb4a10-cda8-4e84-86d6-297da971545d",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, an encounter with a hostile Undead is a rare event. You may never have use for the Claustra runestone. I hope so for your sake.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e0626bfa-1e40-4276-a2b2-c901dc3e5f9f",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, if you do encounter a Wraith or a Revenant, this is the only defensive magic item that you can use directly to stop it. A true Hero needs to be prepared for even the unlikeliest of encounters.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "5ae95194-7a24-4036-96fa-f8ccb7dde45e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "20",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1e94caf4-5c22-442c-aa42-a537614f94ec",
                            "text": "Ask How Claustra Runestones Work",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f24bce44-5d10-4783-b94d-d591ca2d6005",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "How does the Claustra runestone work? If it just blocks the Undead, won't the Undead just move around it?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "bdd623fd-2ab0-47ca-8a4c-cc4c620c2351",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "This is why you must move the runestone towards the creature rather than  just placing the runestone upon the ground. Simply slide the runestone in a graceful manner in the direction of the Undead.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4c77e51e-7d51-47ec-bfca-b96cb4fc451b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Once the magical field of the runestone comes in contact with the Undead creature's aura, the spell is triggered and the creature is trapped for several minutes.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3e6ace68-69bc-4ab0-8396-da2053141ee9",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Unfortunately, the greater Undead like Wraiths may still be able to cast magical spells, so you must avoid them whenever possible. They are extremely dangerous.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "e2e53600-7596-4942-b586-3b664de7e8c6",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "20",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "17b04b04-d5d8-4bae-a539-9e530ce4c9bd",
                            "text": "Make a Joke About Claustra Runestones",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "797f93d6-c53c-4446-890d-50425adf69f4",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What did the Wizard Professor say as he put a Claustra runestone in front of his failing student who had been turned into a Wraith?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "abf7fe0d-276f-405d-a606-48eeffa0a871",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "\"Thou shalt not pass!\"",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "126ee6b3-0c61-45c4-9d77-d4fb997d88cb",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I gather that is some sort of joke?",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "51175154-f732-4e13-9586-8dbc795f7ac3",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Hey, at least it was on topic!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
